milestones.description: Khurram Khan has become the top scorer for UAE in ODIs with 427 runs, going past Amjad Ali's 342
Khurram Khan has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for UAE breaking Amjad Ali's record
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Alhashmi has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shahzad's 2
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Khurram Khan has broken the record for most ODIs (8) as captain for UAE, going past Zarawani
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (40) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
